These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  engineer, freelancer, nurse, writer, librarian
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, apricot, black, blue, lavender
There are 5 different nationalities: british, chinese, egyptian, malaysian, turkish
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person who likes black is on the left of the freelancer##1
 3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the nurse is the nurse##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person who likes ebony##1
 6. the librarian is on the left of the nurse##1
 7. the british is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the writer is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the writer is on the far right##1
10. the engineer is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the librarian is between the chinese and the person who likes lavender##2
12. the malaysian is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
13. the turkish is on the right of the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Job      | engineer        | freelancer | librarian     | nurse   | writer |
| Color   | black     | apricot      | blue | lavender   | ebony    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | chinese     | british | egyptian | turkish  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

