.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, blood-red, azure, yellow, ebony
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, lily, dahlia, rose, daffodil
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the chinese and the person who growsdaffodil##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the indian is the person who growsrose##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growslily##1
11. the indian is the person who likes azure##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Color         | yellow | red | ebony    | blood-red  | azure    |
| Flower   | daffodil    | lily       | dahlia      | tulip | rose        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike | skateboard | scooter | helicopter |

