.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, oliveros, old-henry, bluemaster, aristoff
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, metal, pop, reggae
House: colonial, modern, gothic-revival, craftsman, victorian
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the craftsman house is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
 4. the chaman-smoker is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the modern house##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 8. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
10. the colonial house is the bluemaster-smoker##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the victorian house##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
13. the victorian house is between the aristoff-smoker and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Cigar   | aristoff  | oliveros | chaman | bluemaster | old-henry        |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | gospel      | pop       | reggae       | ambient       |
| House         | modern | victorian  | craftsman    | colonial    | gothic-revival        |

