The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, indie, reggae, rock
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, japanese, pakistani
 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the colonial house is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 4. the pakistani is between the fan of reggae and the person drinking fanta##2
 5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the tower house##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the tower house is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the victorian house is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
10. the fan of reggae is the british##1
11. the townhouse house is on the right of the tower house##1
12. the british is on the right of the fan of indie##1
13. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Beverage          | mirinda  | soy-milk     | fanta   | milk     | juice |
