.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, soy-milk, sprite, water
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, december, october, september, february
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, australian, french, polish, turkish
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, videographer, dressmaker, journalist, musician
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the french##1
 5. the musician is on the right of the accountant##1
 6. the person drinking water is between the person who's birthday is in february and the videographer##2
 7. the dressmaker is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the french##1
10. the journalist is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in february and the videographer##2
12. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the polish##1
13. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | water      | sprite   | fanta   | soy-milk   |
| Birthday   | february    | september   | october   | december | march     |
| Nationality   | argentine | french     | polish   | turkish | australian |
| Job         | accountant | musician | videographer | dressmaker  | journalist     |

