 1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 3. the person drinking tea is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person eating blueberry##2
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in the middle##1
 7. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
 8. the person eating mango is on the far right##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating cucumber##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
13. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
