5 different pets are kept: mouse, bird, pony, horse, lizard
House: palace, wooden, gothic-revival, cottage, cape-cod
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, train, trike, van
 1. the cape-cod house is between the person driving the quad-bike and the wooden house##2
 2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the cottage house##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the owner of the horse##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
10. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the train is between the gothic-revival house and the owner of the pony##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Pet       | lizard | mouse | pony  | horse | bird    |
| House       | gothic-revival        | cottage   | wooden  | cape-cod   | palace |
| Transport   | trike       | train      | van      | motorbike | quad-bike  |

