.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, september, january, april, july
There are 5 different favourite colors: purple, red, green, brown, pink
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, hip-hop, house, trance
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the person who likes brown is between the person watching crime movies and the person who likes green##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who likes brown##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the fan of house##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who likes pink and the fan of blues##2
 7. the fan of house is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
10. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person who likes green is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Birthday      | may      | september         | april      | january | july     |
| Color           | red | green | brown | pink    | purple  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | blues        | ambient   | house    | trance     |

