 2. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the tower house##1
 4. the wooden house is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person eating eggplant and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the farmhouse house and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is cottaged-games##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's hobby is cottaged-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is cottaged-games is on the right of the person eating corn##1

.:: Answer ::.
