| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking  | cooking      | february-climbing |
| Color   | ebony    | brown   | white | light-blue | blood-red   |
| Birthday   | may | april    | february    | august       | november         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 